               <p> In the construction arena, CK&A has skillfully counseled clients whether businesses or individuals in matters pertaining to all aspects of new construction or renovation:  the bidding process, liens, extras and change orders, construction damage claims, payment and job completion claims.</p>  

            <p>We have represented owners, general contractors, subcontractors, sub-subcontractors and suppliers in all types of construction matters. </p> 

            <p>CK&A’s lawyers have prepared and collected mechanic’s lien claims involving such notable Chicagoland properties as the Merchandise Mart, John G. Shedd Aquarium, Chicago Board of Trade, Civic Opera House, Encyclopedia Britannica Building, Michael Reese Hospital and Waukegan Port District.  We also have prepared and enforced, or defended against, mechanic’s lien claims on residential properties.</p>

